text: "Feelings are feelings. They have to come out somewhere," she said about the new album. "I'm a firm believer in that and writing is a really healthy way for you to express your feelings and that's how I've always done it.”
title: Fergie ‘Doing Great’ Following Split With Ex-Husband Josh Duhamel

meta_data.description: The couple recently ended their marriage after eight years together.
